---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AdSlot from '../components/AdSlot.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us - Singapore Business Directory"
  description="Learn about our mission to provide comprehensive information on businesses registered in Singapore."
>
  <section class="bg-white border-b">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">About Singapore Business Directory</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            The Singapore Business Directory is dedicated to providing comprehensive, accurate, and up-to-date information about businesses registered in Singapore. Our mission is to create a transparent business environment by making company information easily accessible to the public.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Whether you're a potential investor, business partner, job seeker, or simply curious about Singapore's business landscape, our directory offers valuable insights into companies operating in the Lion City.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Ad slot in middle of content -->
          <AdSlot id="about-mid-ad" position="about-mid" className="my-8" />
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What We Offer</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Comprehensive Business Database</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
                  Access detailed information on thousands of Singapore-registered businesses, including registration details, company addresses, and industry classifications.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Advanced Search Functionality</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
                  Find exactly what you're looking for with our powerful search tools. Filter by company name, registration type, status, and more.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Business Insights</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
                  Stay informed with our blog and news section, featuring the latest updates on Singapore's business environment, regulatory changes, and market trends.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Data Sources</h2>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Our directory compiles information from various public sources, including:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600 mb-6">
            <li>Accounting and Corporate Regulatory Authority (ACRA)</li>
            <li>Company websites and public announcements</li>
            <li>Other publicly available databases</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            We strive to ensure the accuracy and timeliness of our data, but we recommend verifying critical information through official channels.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Contact Us</h2>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Have questions, suggestions, or feedback? We'd love to hear from you. Please contact us at:
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            <strong>Email:</strong> info@sgbusinessdirectory.com<br>
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +65 6123 4567<br>
            <strong>Address:</strong> 123 Business Avenue, #01-01, Singapore 123456
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Team</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500 sm:mt-4">
          Meet the people behind Singapore Business Directory
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="mx-auto h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/614810/pexels-photo-614810.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
                alt="Team member"
                class="h-full w-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium space-y-1">
                <h3 class="text-gray-900">Alex Tan</h3>
                <p class="text-primary-600">Founder & CEO</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-gray-500">
                <p class="text-sm">
                  Over 15 years of experience in business intelligence and data analytics.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="mx-auto h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/733872/pexels-photo-733872.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
                alt="Team member"
                class="h-full w-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium space-y-1">
                <h3 class="text-gray-900">Michelle Lim</h3>
                <p class="text-primary-600">Data & Research Director</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-gray-500">
                <p class="text-sm">
                  Specialized in corporate research and business intelligence.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="mx-auto h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/91227/pexels-photo-91227.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
                alt="Team member"
                class="h-full w-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium space-y-1">
                <h3 class="text-gray-900">Rajesh Kumar</h3>
                <p class="text-primary-600">Technology Lead</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-gray-500">
                <p class="text-sm">
                  Expert in web development and data management systems.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>